item.title: Natalie Portman
item.description:
Is it your brown hair
that makes me need more air?

Is your tense face
the reason I'm lost in space?

For your sense of style
most would run a mile
not to mention your smile,
which makes any chore worthwhile ...

Every word you say
sounds just like the birds in May,
after the April showers
have brought forth the flowers.

And your divine intelligence
only adds to your radiance.

Natalie Portman thank you
for being you, and not Lou.

Note: 'Lou' refers to Captain Lou Albano.
